<plot>Months after Nicole (Marthe Keller) loses all track of her problematic son Guillaume ( Dimitri Storoge), he reappears all of a sudden, announcing he's about to marry a rich woman. He affirms he has rid himself of his longtime drug problem, and asks his mother (a master chef) to offer a grand banquet in honor of the new couple. This leads her to jail, and to many decisions she will make in the name of love. Thus, the original titles "Par Amour" and "Je reclaim la prison (France - working title): Out of love, and I'm asking for jail, respectively. Nicole is a generous soul, offering her love to family and cell mates alike.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?422729</url></doc>
